## Limitations

The findings in this report are based on a limited selection of articles and may not encompass all perspectives on the topic. Additionally, the articles reviewed are from a specific timeframe and may not reflect the most current research or diverse viewpoints. Further research could provide a more comprehensive understanding of how failure leads to success across different contexts and industries.